org.spongepowered.api.world.schematic

Interface Schematic

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ArchetypeVolume, BlockVolume, MutableBlockVolume

    public interface Schematic
extends ArchetypeVolume
    A special archetype volume designed to be persisted. Contains additional metadata to assist with this persistence.

        default Optional<MutableBiomeVolume> getBiomes()
        Gets the MutableBiomeVolume of this schematic. As biomes are optionally included and not required, they may be optionally excluded. If the schematic would contain them, they will be present during deserialization via DataTranslator.
